data.description: What a beauty with wonderful updates throughout located on a tree shaded corner lot with an indoor pool, great outdoor entertaining area & green space. Love the contemporary vibe of this home! Windows w/ natural light, two living rooms, high ceilings in the entry & den. Formal dining room off the entry. Beautiful kitchen w/ quartz counters, marble back splash, drop in farm sink, Jenn-air appliances, double ovens, microwave drawer, gas cook top, custom cabinetry, informal dining area, doors to the patio, and more! Owner's suite downstairs and a stunning bathroom w/ jetted tub & stone accent wall, large walk-in shower, and enclosed courtyard patio. Off the kitchen is a study or 4th bedroom, spacious laundry room with sink and closet. Upstairs: 2 guest bedroom with shared full bathroom, and 2 game rooms or media room. Large covered pool with full bathroom, patio with arbor, and seating area. Opposite the pool in a grassy area. The garage has a Trane portable a/c.
